<div id="changing-the-default-address-book">
<section id="section-4.2">
        <h3 id="name-changing-the-default-addres"><a href="#section-4.2">4.2.&nbsp;&nbsp;Changing the default address book</a></h3>
<p id="section-4.2-1">The client tries to change the default address book from "Personal" to "Autosaved" (and makes no other change):<a href="#section-4.2-1" class="pilcrow">¶</a></p>
<div class="alignLeft art-text artwork" id="section-4.2-2">
<pre>[
  ["AddressBook/set", {
    "accountId": "a0x9",
    "onSuccessSetIsDefault": "cd40089d-35f9-4fd7-980b-ba3a9f1d74fe"
  }, "0"]
]
</pre><a href="#section-4.2-2" class="pilcrow">¶</a>
</div>
<p id="section-4.2-3">The server allows the change, returning the following response:<a href="#section-4.2-3" class="pilcrow">¶</a></p>
<div class="alignLeft art-text artwork" id="section-4.2-4">
<pre>[
  ["AddressBook/set", {
    "accountId": "a0x9",
    "updated": {
      "cd40089d-35f9-4fd7-980b-ba3a9f1d74fe": {
        "isDefault": true
      },
      "062adcfa-105d-455c-bc60-6db68b69c3f3": {
        "isDefault": false
      }
    }
  }, "0"]
]
</pre><a href="#section-4.2-4" class="pilcrow">¶</a>
</div>
</section>
</div>
</section>
